,"year":-1308},{"id":"recuuYBbjik6sSSSb","ref":"Ruth.1.7","text":"Wherefore she went forth out of the place where she was, and her two daughters in law with her; and they went on the way to return unto the land of Judah.","year":-1308},{"id":"recHYjh5SGhFvVkYg","ref":"Ruth.1.8","text":"And Naomi said unto her two daughters in law, Go, return each to her mother’s house: the LORD deal kindly with you, as ye have dealt with the dead, and with me.","year":-1308}]}
